    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/b68ba858f87b549f7cbf6bfbd5efe6bd.avif?t=1749155224\" width=618 height=91 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jin &amp; Jan: A ghostly souls-like puzzle game with dual inverse control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jin &amp; Jan, </strong>in an act of<strong> </strong>mischief, splitted the world in two: the Light World and the Dark World. Now, the intrepid ghost brothers will have to bring back the balance to the world in an exciting adventure that combines <strong>puzzle and skill</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Jin follows your instructions</strong>, but his twin Jan <strong>always move to the opposite.</strong> You will need to plan every step carefully, since the enemies react to your movements: some of them move in real time and the others move as you take action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jin and Jan will take you through increasingly difficult levels, <strong>where you will be defeated and learn</strong>. Every challenge surpassed will take you a little closer to mastering this peculiar duo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/7211b8c77e7cb4b496556a513626d026.avif?t=1749155224\" width=618 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind-bending puzzles</strong>: Test your brain with puzzles that require coordination and strategic thinking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/650d8dec741c42bee4307611ce08d5cf.poster.avif?t=1749155224\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/650d8dec741c42bee4307611ce08d5cf.webm?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/650d8dec741c42bee4307611ce08d5cf.mp4?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intuitive controls</strong>: Jin &amp; Jan are easy to control, but mastering them is an art. Learn to anticipate Jan's movements and use his stubbornness to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/ef1bb287a3eab39737b68550df66d8a8.poster.avif?t=1749155224\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/ef1bb287a3eab39737b68550df66d8a8.webm?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/ef1bb287a3eab39737b68550df66d8a8.mp4?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenges Levels</strong>: 45 challenging levels await you to test your mind and skill. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/9883b50e5984eac231393d2413b3bd7c.poster.avif?t=1749155224\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/9883b50e5984eac231393d2413b3bd7c.webm?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/9883b50e5984eac231393d2413b3bd7c.mp4?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun for all ages: </strong>Jin &amp; Jan is a game suitable for all ages, perfect for playing alone or with friends and family.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/5cb7303b4fe6a50823f49c5a9ec6d6ae.poster.avif?t=1749155224\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/5cb7303b4fe6a50823f49c5a9ec6d6ae.webm?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/5cb7303b4fe6a50823f49c5a9ec6d6ae.mp4?t=1749155224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/7cf32df22b77faef4094282287c1b357.avif?t=1749155224\" width=618 height=115 /></span></p>",
